<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 — Page Not Found | FashionZone</title>
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --fz-gold: #c9a96e;
            --fz-gold-hover: #b8985d;
            --fz-dark: #1a1a2e;
            --fz-dark-2: #16213e;
            --fz-white: #fafafa;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--fz-dark) 0%, var(--fz-dark-2) 100%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            color: var(--fz-white);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: -20%;
            left: -10%;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        body::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20%;
            right: -10%;
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .error-container {
            text-align: center;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
            padding: 60px 40px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
            box-shadow: 0 32px 64px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 90%;
            animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .error-code {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
            color: var(--fz-gold);
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 30%, var(--fz-gold) 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            letter-spacing: -2px;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--fz-white);
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            margin-bottom: 35px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .home-link {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            background-color: var(--fz-gold);
            color: #1a1a2e;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.25);
            transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
        }

        .home-link:hover {
            background-color: var(--fz-gold-hover);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(201, 169, 110, 0.35);
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        .home-link:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <h1 class="error-code">404</h1>
        <h2 class="error-title">Page Not Found</h2>
        <p class="error-message">The curated collection or page you are looking for has either been moved or is temporarily unavailable.</p>
        <a href="/" class="home-link">Back to Homepage</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>